The leather used would be high-quality and have a matte finish, similar to the texture of Bottega's Intrecciato woven leather.

The handles and trim of the bag would be made from the same woven leather as Bottega's iconic bags, creating a luxurious and tactile contrast to the puzzle-like body. The hardware on the bag, such as the zippers and clasps, would be kept simple and minimal to let the unique texture of the bag speak for itself.

The interior of the bag would feature multiple compartments and pockets, as well as a soft suede lining in a complementary color. Overall, the combination of the Loewe Puzzle Bag design and Bottega texture would create a stunning and functional handbag that is both eye-catching and sophisticated.
